{"tid":2408721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国發現新物種  冠名「古天樂」","createTime":"2021-02-15T08:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T09:12:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd99adfb62e3c2f2c959f0709447639ce57e7761","tid":2408721,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"中國西南地區發現新的昆蟲物種「胡古叉襀」，其中「胡古」這個名字的由來，竟然是科學家為了感謝藝人胡歌、古天樂對當地環境保護與基礎教育事業做出的貢獻，而特別取兩人的姓氏來命名。<br />\n<br />\n環球時報報導，生態學領域期刊「世界生態學」日前刊登了一篇名為「中國四川省叉襀屬（襀翅目：叉襀科）一新種」的文章，內容提到，這個在甘孜藏族自治州發現的叉襀科新物種，遵循了「國際動物命名規約」（第四版）第31.1.2條款，以胡歌姓名的拼音「Hu Ge」、古天樂姓名的拼音「Koo Tin-lok」加上拉丁化後綴「-orum」命名，全名為「胡古叉襀」（Nemoura hugekootinlokorum Wang &amp; Meng, sp. nov.）。<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，胡歌和古天樂兩人，可謂娛樂圈低調做慈善做公益的典範。胡歌2013年受邀成為斑頭雁守護與調查項目的形象代言人。此後幾乎每一年，胡歌都會去三江源進行公益活動，挑水、植樹、撿垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n胡歌2020年還參加了守護G7公路的生態公益項目。G7公路是世界上穿越沙漠最長的高速公路，為了改善沿途荒漠化的自然環境，胡歌和公益項目的其他志願者一同前往內蒙古額濟納旗，參與一年一度的春季種植。<br />\n<br />\n此外，去年疫情期間，胡歌還向武漢兒童醫院捐贈了100台空氣消毒機等近百萬的醫療用品。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，根據香港慈恩基金會官網數據顯示，自2008年汶川地震後，古天樂建立慈善基金會，12年間已經援助建校超過120多所。即使在去年疫情期間，古天樂慈善基金會仍援建了6所學校。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/paper/2021/02/15/11667096.png&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=400&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Fpaper%2F2021%2F02%2F15%2F11667096.png%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D400%26nt%3D1&h=63f4067c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國新發現的物種「胡古叉襀」。（取材自環球時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/5251639\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F5251639&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=8d03e726\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/5251639</a>"},{"pid":"ec45a33ebe98aaf67282328d44368bd51b70b3b0","tid":2408721,"uid":46587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"有冇習近平"},{"pid":"36e6a06a8173b6db4dd9348818a64158beab5ff9","tid":2408721,"uid":215755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"大陸咁有錢<br />\n洗撚佢捐咩"},{"pid":"c58e70582a4de1fdeaa8d22b460dc071734ef724","tid":2408721,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"依隻係自然界新物種定係支那製造出嚟嘅新物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aeb9ab74be5e90ab82e2aee5f8c2b554faf9ef7","tid":2408721,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ec45a33ebe98aaf67282328d44368bd51b70b3b0","tid":2408721,"uid":46587,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"有冇習近平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/13195424/1468410287729.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2F13195424%2F1468410287729.png&h=fd30c3c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06992943ba7f045126789bc62dba8a7a5fcdb466","tid":2408721,"uid":39470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:00:09.000Z","msg":"Huge Kootinlok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSo Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236c1e7accbeff31d783b4caf45a7b9bfaa75125","tid":2408721,"uid":198278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F60HMFh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF60HMFh.png&h=8ba4b14e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}